      <extensionElements>
         <signavio:signavioDiagramMetaData metaKey="meta-processdescription" metaValue="Receive consignment stock with the same procedure as for purchased stock. It is, however, assigned a special stock type of 'K'. This causes the stock to be counted within the ERP inventory database but separately from 'owned' stock and it is not valuated for the plant. Goods Receipt into Org. premises without changing the ownership of materials from vendor to Org Includes initiating consignment blocks where necessary."/>
